summary: Hello! I need help to raise money to save myself and my family from losing our house and starvation. Though I do not want to go...
caption:
Hello! I need help to raise money to save myself and my family from losing our house and starvation. Though I do not want to go into the details, due to wanting to keep my life private, the basics are that my father was unable to work for a week due to spinal problems and has since then been dealing with receiving less work. I have done my best in looking for a job, but we live in a city that is economically terrible so I haven’t had much luck.

This is my final resort.

My specialties are digital work and watercolors, so you can specify if you want it a specific way. To look over my work you may check my Deviantart (https://www.deviantart.com/happymaskprince) , and the “my art” tag on my tumblr.

Prices

Head shots/icons

  • Sketch - $5
  • Line - $7
  • Color - $10
  • Extra Character + $2

Bust

  • Sketch -: $10
  • Line - $12
  • Color - $18
  • Extra Character + $3

Full Body

  • Sketch - $15
  • Line$18
  • Flat Color - $20
  • Full Color - $25
  • Extra Character + $5
